HUNTINGTON NATL. BANK
v.
CPW PROPERTIES, LTD. 2018-0668 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW O'Donnell, J., dissents.

Kennedy, J., dissents and would accept the appeal and consolidate the cause with 2018-0667, Huntington Natl. Bank v. CPW Properties, Ltd.
